    "description": "An M5 depth-train lane carries a Stable (or LTS) public claim only when its proof packet is current within its freshness SLO, evidence has not expired, backport policy is defined and the window is open, and owner sign-off is present. A lane that loses any of those must drop below the cutline rather than inherit an adjacent green lane."
